140
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,120
What would you like?

141
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,200
Go ahead.

142
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,240
Yes.

143
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,400
Do you remember

144
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,480
