146
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,850
You only ate

147
00:09:37,850 --> 00:09:39,440
the plum blossom cakes I made.

148
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,360
You can go now.

149
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:43,840
