169
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:00,640
Yes, it's good.

170
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:03,200
♪Hold tighter♪

171
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:05,120
♪But I've already♪

172
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,100
♪Decided to forget you♪

173
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:07,960
It's beautiful.

174
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,040
♪But♪

175
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:14,920
♪But♪

176
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:31,440
♪Those things about you♪

177
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:35,440
Governor, is there anything else you need?

